<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" dir="RTL" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-align: right; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed; margin: 0in .5in 8.0pt 0in;"><span lang="AR-SY" style="font-family: 'MTN Brighter Sans Arabic'; mso-bidi-language: AR-SY;">الرسالة : </span><span dir="LTR" lang="EN-GB" style="font-family: 'MTN Brighter Sans Arabic'; mso-bidi-language: AR-SY;">You spent x SMS and your account now is xx SYP</span><span lang="AR-SY" style="font-family: 'MTN Brighter Sans Arabic'; mso-bidi-language: AR-SY;"> .</span></p>
